question: Within a radius of 100 kilometers, where can I find  a café in the direction of IIT Stuart School of Business, Chicago, IL from Zao Island, Valparaiso, IN?
sql:
WITH
    angle AS (SELECT degrees(ST_Azimuth(ST_GeomFromText('POINT (-87.067399 41.458418)',4326)::geography, ST_GeomFromText('POINT (-87.642109 41.879101)',4326)::geography)) AS value)
SELECT * FROM pois,angle
WHERE amenity = 'cafe'
AND ST_DWithin(pois.geometry, ST_GeomFromText('POINT (-87.067399 41.458418)',4326)::geography, 100000)
AND (degrees(ST_Azimuth(ST_GeomFromText('POINT (-87.067399 41.458418)',4326)::geography, pois.geometry)) BETWEEN angle.value - 22.5 AND angle.value + 22.5);
